{"tid":239409,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我周柏豪，想送呢首歌比部分連登仔","createTime":"2017-05-11T16:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T19:21:24.000Z","uid":62717,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee4d86cffe90c9195552229b7cef8621e9939a7","tid":239409,"uid":62717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5O5M4WF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5O5M4WF.jpg&h=e9b90af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n逐漸逐漸被粉碎<br />\n城內每個報攤　已經有人列隊<br />\n被社會抄家　再被網絡凌辱<br />\n群眾不需審判　判死他有罪<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">然後　你用最毒那字句　讓他永不超生<br />\n卸下責任　繼續你人生</span><br />\n<br />\n平台有呼聲叫他跳下來　連隨有道德判官趕過來<br />\n［red]人人也歡呼拍手湊熱鬧　說他死不足惜　再不可忍耐[/red]<br />\n絕望裡的他看不見未來　墮下那刻聽見一千句活該<br />\n你看著爛肉　說他死不悔改<br />\n<br />\n你不准他悔改<br />\n<br />\n自問犯下甚麼錯<br />\n淪落到要處斬　撲熄世人怒火<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">還有一堆恥笑　大眾在娛樂<br />\n面對他的死相　笑得很磊落<br />\n然後　你尚要逐句逐句　讓他永不超生<br />\n卸下責任　泯滅你良心<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">平台有呼聲叫他跳下來　同場有道德判官的主宰<br />\n人人也歡呼拍手湊熱鬧　說他死不足惜　如預計之內</span><br />\n絕望裡的他看不見未來　墮下那刻聽見一千句活該<br />\n你看著地獄　說他死不悔改<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n你已經將他割開　叫他怎麼悔改?</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B9zd3e4Rlio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB9zd3e4Rlio&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=8f987788\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B9zd3e4Rlio</a>"},{"pid":"55fcae727a614f4724f7b882e04cbb4f113711f2","tid":239409,"uid":3845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98fda0b54332924d0c1eaf147c10c196797b91be","tid":239409,"uid":62717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aad55fe5862626c7c578f27b37fa26545d93a5c","tid":239409,"uid":62717,"l